{"tid":2450591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍門冰室飯卷計劃 同區議員合作 學生 老人 窮人都有份","createTime":"2021-03-17T13:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T16:22:46.000Z","uid":21545,"like":37,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"64316be5ff70f141ae844b3589a512eda25d8153","tid":2450591,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"【 撐弱勢・撐瓏門 】<br />\n<br />\n是咁的⋯<br />\n我哋一直好努力學習緊<br />\n點樣好好分配大家留低嘅飯券<br />\n<br />\n暫時⋯我哋已經搵咗一啲「同路人」區議員<br />\n幫手聯絡區內有經濟困難嘅香港人<br />\n嚟到瓏門食飯<br />\n<br />\n雖然仲係有唔少客人表示<br />\n瓏門不如keep返起啲券<br />\n穩定返個現金流 先派飯<br />\n<br />\n但係 我真係唔想喺不勞而獲之下<br />\nKeep住你哋啲錢<br />\n咁倒不如放返落學生/區議員手上啦<br />\n幫到瓏門之餘 又幫到社會上有需要嘅人<br />\n<br />\n好感激 每一位出過手幫瓏門嘅朋友<br />\n嚟緊子 我會好努力頂住<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 💭💭💭<br />\n我哋建議學生們最好親身嚟拎飯券🙏🏻<br />\n始終呢啲券都係哥哥姐姐<br />\n用自己荷包 真金白銀買畀你哋<br />\n我哋真係好希望呢啲券唔會被濫用<br />\n所以你哋乖 自己嚟拎喇<br />\n<br />\n而家佢哋有搵區議員合作 應該會安排好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 龍門真係告急都不忘回饋香港人 真係好傻"},{"pid":"fbb1c015e2f8bf682681796b972e32c81ae658e4","tid":2450591,"uid":106290,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"5686ce4f2ec43f3a72ecaf66c36ef785d500d4b3","tid":2450591,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06424cbd975a88b08a953ffdd860459601fdca6","tid":2450591,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5686ce4f2ec43f3a72ecaf66c36ef785d500d4b3","tid":2450591,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gi